    # ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZZ

    ${stdout}  ${stderr}=  Execute Command
    ...  ${XCAT_DIR_PATH}/nodels ${group}  return_stderr=True
    Should Be Empty  ${stderr}

